727690f-b.title: Queens: Powells Cove Bouleva - 6th Avenue
727690f-b.text:
Powells Cove Boulevard, east from near 6th Avenue, White-
stone, showing three views of the Whitestone Landing area on
the East River.
P. L. Sperr  April 13, 1927
NO REPRODUCTIONS  Views 1,2,3
